OL,3,CHolidays: Get Away For Less
OL,5,FIn this episode of Tonight, Helen
OL,6,FSkelton looks into the tricks and tips
OL,7,Fto help you bag a bargain break,
OL,8,Fwhilst also making sure you don't fall
OL,9,Fvictim to the rising number of holiday
OL,10,Fscams.
OL,12,FWe'll meet savvy travellers like
OL,13,FChelsea Dickenson who's made a name
OL,14,Ffor herself as the Cheap Holiday
OL,15,FExpert, as well as viral TikToker Josh
OL,16,FKerr, who worked out that it's cheaper
OL,17,Ffor him to live in an all inclusive
OL,18,Fresort in Turkey than his Manchester
OL,19,Fflat.
