OL,3,CHolidays: Get Away For Less
OL,5,FHelen meets Mum of four Leanda
OL,6,FParrott, who came across a listing on
OL,7,Fsocial media for a bargain holiday
OL,8,Fcottage in East Sussex. After chatting
OL,9,Fwith the private seller, she booked
OL,10,Fthe cottage as a family break. But
OL,11,Fafter a two and a half hour drive, she
OL,12,Farrived at the address to find it was
OL,13,Fnot really a holiday cottage, but a
OL,14,Ffamily home being fraudulently let out
OL,15,Fonline by a stranger.
OL,17,FIf you're one of the reported 29% of
OL,18,FBrits planning to go on more holidays
OL,19,Fin 2024, take some time to do your
OL,20,Fresearch, follow expert advice, and
OL,21,Fsee if you can get away for less.
